  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the effect of Ivabradine vs Atenolol on heart rate and
      effort tolerance in patients with mild to moderate mitral stenosis and normal sinus rhythm.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
